name: Bontoc, Mt. Province 2021
description:
Post-interactive art see the link (https://bit.ly/3pVyVQw)

Summer apostolate, an community immersion in Bontoc, Mountain Province, the immersion area is in the two community, the Sitio Mainit and Sitio Tocucan. Both community has a guidance from the parish church of Bontoc, Mountain Province. The project is based on the mission of church, entitled Youth in Mission: Beloved. Gifted. Empowered. The prepared module is composed of Christian-Filipino values, it is integration of Christian faith through Art, that help the youth to know themselves.
